com.intel.icecp.cli.util

Class PartialChannelsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.cli.util.PartialChannelsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.intel.icecp.core.management.Channels

    public class PartialChannelsImpl
extends Object
implements com.intel.icecp.core.management.Channels
    Implementation of Channels; this is a minimal implementation used for providing channels while sharing a small (see CORE_POOL_SIZE) thread pool. It expects channel providers to be SPI-provided or registered statically on ImplementationLoader.
